b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2144,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding an Issue with Close-Range Manacaster Force Strikes","message":"<div>We have confirmed an issue with adventurers who use close-range manacasters that causes their force strikes to reduce the overdrive gauge of an enemy in the break state more than intended.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We will address this issue by correcting the amount that the overdrive gauge is reduced; there will be no changes made to the power of the force strikes themselves. In addition, since this issue only affects close-range manacasters, there will be no changes made to the force strikes of long-range or rapid-fire manacasters.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Once this issue has been addressed in a data update around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1619589600\\"><\/span>, we will send a goodwill gesture of 120 wyrmite to players who started playing before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1619589599\\"><\/span>. This goodwill gesture can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after logging in.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1619071200,"prev_article_id":"2143","next_article_id":"2134","image_path":"","update_time":1619061712}}}'